title: Easy Bake in a Bottle? Testing our NEW Easy Bake Setting Spray
description:
Hey my loves! 🩷 Introducing EASY BAKE SETTING SPRAY, aka Easy Bake in a bottle 🤭

We took our iconic Easy Bake Powder and turned it into a fixing spray that locks in your glam while keeping your skin looking airbrushed, fresh, and ultra-blurred for 16 HOURS ⏳
We worked SO hard to bottle that Easy Bake flawless matte finish into a setting spray that’s lightweight, breathable, and packed with skin-loving ingredients—but we DID IT!

 الترجمة متوفرة

Why you NEED this in your routine:
🌾 Rice Starch & Mineral Clay: Controls shine for that soft-matte, oil-free finish
💧 5 forms of Hyaluronic Acid: Deeply hydrates + refreshes skin
🔒 Transfer-proof formula: Locks in your makeup for up to 16 HOURS
🚫 Alcohol-free, fragrance-free: Gentle enough for ALL skin types, including sensitive skin
 
This hydrating setting spray is perfect for dry skin, sensitive skin, and mature skin, with a lightweight, non-comedogenic formula that won’t clog pores. Whether you need a makeup fixing spray, a setting spray for sensitive skin, or a finishing spray for a dewy, long-lasting look, this is IT. SHAKE WELL and spray for fresh, flawless makeup that actually lasts!

title: HOW TO MASTER YOUR COMPLEXION ROUTINE!
description:
F**K FILTERS…  Seriously, this complexion routine will give you that filter-like finish that lasts ALL. DAY. LONG!
الترجمة العربية متوفرة
 
Hey, beautiful people!
I have been getting quite a few requests asking me for my FULL complexion routine so I had to film it for you all. I’m about to spill EVERYTHING!!
 
Over the last 14 years, I've picked up tons of beauty secrets as a blogger, editor, and makeup artist, but above all, as a beauty lover!! I’ve learned from the world's top artists, and trust me, after a lot of trial and error, I've found the MOST foolproof complexion routine ever. From how to prep your skin to the best makeup tools to blend your makeup like a pro. Boo, I've got you covered.
 
P.S. – I’ve added a wear test at the end of the video so you can see just how flawless this complexion routine looks, after all day wear… in Dubai's heat (and yes, it’s REALLY hot here)!

Here are the products I used:
✨ Yo Glow AHA & BHA Facial Enzyme Scrub: https://hudabeauty.com/default/wishful/yo-glow-enzyme-scrub-40ml-WF00002.html
✨ WISHFUL Honey Whip Peptide Moisturizer
✨ Easy Blur Silicone-Free Smoothing Primer: https://hudabeauty.com/default/primer/easy-blur-silicone-free-smoothing-primer-HB01342.html
✨ Easy Blur Foundation: https://hudabeauty.com/default/foundation/easy-blur-foundation-macchiato-400g-HB01166.html
✨ Easy Blur Base Brush: https://hudabeauty.com/default/brushes/easy-blur-foundation-brush-HB01362.html
✨ #FAUXFILTER Color Corrector in Cherry Blossom: https://hudabeauty.com/default/huda-beauty/fauxfilter-color-corrector-HB01025.html
✨ #FAUXFILTER Concealer in Sugar Biscuit: https://hudabeauty.com/default/ff-collection/fauxfilter-luminous-matte-concealer-HB00867.html
✨ Blush Filter Liquid Blush in Cotton Candy and Strawberry Cream: https://hudabeauty.com/default/blush/blush-filter-liquid-blush-HB01345.html
✨ Easy Bake Loose Baking & Setting Powder: https://hudabeauty.com/default/powder-and-setting-spray/easy-bake-loose-baking-and-setting-powder-HB00142.html

Love you all so much! Hope you enjoy this video. Let me know what you want to see next.

title: MY BEST-KEPT COMPLEXION SECRET: THE EASY ROUTINE
description:
Hey beautiful people!! 💖 I’m fiiiinally revealing our BEST-kept secret…and I am so happy to share, our EASY family is GROWING! 🌟
الترجمة العربية متوفرة
 
Meet our newest babies…. EASY BLUR PRIMER and EASY BLUR FOUNDATION!!!
Created to be used with our Best-Selling EASY BAKE, we wanted to give you the most beautiful no-filter-needed-ultra-blurred effect!
 
The three of these products together make up our new EASY ROUTINE!! Prime + Blur + Bake = The most blurred skin ever!!!
 
When I stopped using Filters in 2021, I had NO idea it was going to change how we make products, but now I am SOOOO happy we made that commitment bc I literally feel these products and the new EASY ROUTINE will give you SO much confidence and make you feel your absolute BEST, which I hope you feel every day!!!
 
I can’t wait for you guys to try the EASY ROUTINE… who knew complexion could be as easy as 1, 2, 3?

title: HUDA BEAUTY: THE REBRAND
description:
Hey beautiful people!! 💖 I am SO excited to share the FIRST episode of our NEW docuseries, giving you a SNEAK PEEK into life inside Huda Beauty during a super special time as we REBRAND Huda Beauty. 
 
It's been such a journey over the past 11 years, but it felt like the right time to refresh the business so it reflects who we are now and where we want to go. It's been hard to say goodbye... but it's time.
 
Of course, during such a momentous moment, we had to take you along this journey with us. We're SO grateful for you all, and we hope you love our rebrand as much as we do. 💕✨
 
Stay tuned for all the raw, real, and emotional moments — from unveiling the new logo to discontinuing products, to shoot days, events, office pranks... Literally we're sharing it ALL!

title: REVEALED! Our Best Palette Yet! EMPOWERED | !أفضل باليت من هدى بيوتي حتى اليوم
description:
Hey beautiful people! I am so excited to share this palette with you.

When I started my journey in the beauty industry, I never knew it would take me this deep into understanding who I really am. The truth is, we all are born powerful, but we allow people to tell us who we are & how far we can go. Whether we listen to it or not, it’s hard not to let it chip away at us & sometimes, we allow ourselves to be defined by others & that limits us. 

I want you to free yourself of any limiting beliefs that you have & to know that you’re capable of the unimaginable, and that you can become everything you have ever dreamed. 

You guys know our big palettes have been a form of self-expression for me & our EM(POWER)ED collection is an exploration of self-love & acceptance. It’s about allowing yourself to embrace every aspect of who you are & unlocking that superpower, that potential, that magic that is in every single one of us. The new EM(POWER)ED Collection is here to remind you just how powerful you truly are!
  
 I am so excited for you all to OWN your own power 💖

#EMPOWERED✨  #LaunchingOctober3 WORLDWIDE!!

title: The story behind our #FAUXFILTER Concealer (BTS) | القصة وراء كونسيلر فو فلتر
description:
Taking you guys with me behind the scenes on the making of our latest complexion baby, #FAUXFILTER LUMINOUS MATTE CONCEALER campaign video!! I’m SOO excited to share this video with you guys! Beauty standards are a social construct—why should anyone get to define what is & isn’t beautiful? We, at Huda Beauty, believe it's up to YOU to define beauty and lift others up along the way. We don’t want you to hide behind makeup, but to use it as a tool of empowerment. YOU are BEAUTY and we want to celebrate you, every shade of you #makeyourmove 

سآخذكم معي اليوم وراء الكواليس لجلسة تصويرالحملة الدعائية  لمنتجنا الجديد فو فلتر لومينوس مات كونسيلر!! أنا متحمسة جداً لمشاركتكم هذا الفيديو! معايير الجمال هي تركيبة مجتمعية - لمَ يحق لإي شخص أن يحدد ما هو جميل وما هو ليس كذلك؟ نحن في هدى بيوتي، تؤمن أنّك أنت من يحدد مفهوم الجمال ويرفع من شأن الآخرين في الوقت عينه. لا نريدك أن تختبئي وراء طبقات المكياج بل أن تستخدميه كوسيلة لتمكين ذاتك. أنت الجمال ونريد أن نحتفل بك، بكل لون من ألوانك.

title: My Blepharoplasty (eyelid surgery) in a bottle | عملية رأب الجفن في قارورة
description:
Hey My Loves!! I hope you guys are ready for this launch, because your eyes will LOVE you! 👁👁

Here it is!!! Our NEW Wishful Eye Lift & Contour Serum, that tightens, lifts, brightens the skin around your eyes, basically it’s a bleph in a bottle! I have been SOO excited to share this with you! I started working on this in 2018, before we actually launched Wishful and I was shook how much some powerful ingredients could tighten the (very thin) skin around your eyes! 

I've been using the final product for almost 2 years now, I call it a Bleph in a bottle! I apply this ON TOP of my eyes, not just the bottom, and it's the first thing I put on every single day, and the last thing I put on at night. I'm at the point where I don't want to be without it. I feel like it's restored my eyelids, I feel fresh, I look awake! It’s also helped me with my dark circles thanks to the caffeine in it which help boost circulation in the area around the eyes (I am obsessed with the ingredients we have in this for the eye area)! 

I can't wait for you all to try this, and to see how it works for you my loves 💕 #Launching23May on hudabeauty.com and all other retailers!

*Please note results vary from person to person #WishfulEyeLift

title: WISHFUL TURNS 2 & WE'RE DOING A HUGE GIVEAWAY!!! | أصبح عمر ويشفول ٢ + مسابقة كبيرة
description:
OMG!!! WISHFUL IS 2 YEARS OLD!!!! I can't believe it's been 2 YEARS since we launched and our baby, Wishful Yo Glow! Literally, the best scrub that I have used and spent YEARS making 🎉

After years of struggling with my skin, launching a skincare line was such a dream for me to share with all of you who may have also struggled to find something simple gentle and effective! Creating a line that was SUPER gentle, wouldn’t break me out (since almost everything does) and actually make my skin improve in texture and appearance took years to develop, but I’m so happy that so many of you tell us how much Wishful has changed your lives and made you feel more confident in your own skin, whether it’s from using our products or just in appreciation of our stance on showing real skin and not using makeup, photoshop and filters in our ads! 

NO Photoshopping, NO filters, just real results on REAL SKIN. It’s been incredible to build this community together and I love you guys SOOO much!!! You guys are the reason we created this line, after telling us everything you wanted from a skincare line, reading all of our skincare posts on my blog over the past 12 years (believe it or not, we post more about skin than makeup), I am so grateful seeing you guys post all your love and results from using Wishful!

#YoGlow is my holy grail exfoliator! I use this literally almost every day! It was created for all skin types to help clear impurities and give you an EXTREME glow.

I want to say a HUGE thank you for always supporting Wishful, for sharing your reviews, tagging us in your posts, and for shouting about us EVERYWHERE. I could not be prouder of this gorgeous community we’ve created!

To celebrate 2 years of @wishfulskin and #YoGlow I will be doing a HUGE GIVEAWAY with a 1-year supply of Yo Glow!!! Like and share this video, comment below and subscribe to my channel for the chance to win! 10 lucky winners will be chosen at random and announced on Feb 16th! Good luck my loves 💛!!!

title: REVEALING! Huda Beauty Rose Quartz Palette & Collection!!! | مجموعة روز كوارتز الجديدة!
description:
Hey my loves!!!! As you guys know self-love has been a JOURNEY for me, one I didn't know I needed, and wasn't even sure I was ready for. I have spoken openly about it over the past few years, whether it was me realizing I didn't love myself, or dealing with my self worth issues, I believe it is something that we all have, which is why I want to share my story openly so we can all learn to love ourselves a little bit more together. Every year when we launch our big palette and I put my heart and soul into them! After I moved to my new house, and my Feng Shui master had recommended that I put Rose Quartz everywhere, I felt so empowered and inspired by the energy and healing powers of Rose Quartz that I wanted to dedicate such an important palette to Rose Quartz and it’s beautiful power! I call Rose Quartz the love stone because that’s literally what it is, it helps with healing, self acceptance and unconditional love!

I wanted to infuse a palette and collection with the same love & energy to empower all of us to love ourselves every single day. Introducing our #RoseQuartz collection #LaunchingNovember1st

💕Rose Quartz Palette 💕
18 shades, made up of powerfully pigmented mattes, multi-shimmer marble creams, insane duo-chrome formulas, innovative metallics with serious sparkle and a ‘crushed stone’ pearly gloss hybrid.

💕Rose Quartz Face Gloss 💕
Slippery is back and BIGGER than ever!! With stunning gold and pink pearls that gives THE SEXIEST, sheer rosy glow.

💕Silk Balm Rose Quartz Illuminating Lip Balm💕
Infused with real rose quartz powder and added gorgeous pink & gold pearls that add a beautiful shimmer and look SO SEXY! 

💕@wishfulskin Rose Quartz Lift & Glow Peel-Off Mask💕
Lift, brighten, tighten & smooth your skin while unclogging your pores! I’m obsessed with the luxe, iridescent formula that peels off in one piece.

Sign up and join the waitlist to make sure you don't miss a thing: https://bit.ly/3DZpjK0

title: Our new liner is SO EASY, SUPER PRECISE, & INSANELY LONG-LASTING!\ كحل جديد سهل ودقيق
description:
Hey my loves! Do you guys remember our OG Life Liner? It was super long-lasting, the most matte, most black liner out there - I was OBSESSED, so now we’ve created the EASIEST liner I’ve ever used. Introducing the LIFE LINER - QUICK 'N EASY Liquid Liner. 

Why are we coming out with a new liner? Liner originated from the Middle East, so it's not a surprise I've been wearing liner since I was 12 which means 25 years, and for that reason I am obsessed with liner, literally it's in my blood. I know some people are really afraid of using liner so we really wanted to make it as easy-to-use as possible for everyone - beginners and pros - that’s why the tip is so fine (0.03mm!!), to give you maximum control!

That’s not all my loves, Life Liner Quick N Easy is also:
⏰Lasts all day
⚫Ultra-black with shade ‘Very Vanta’ 
💧Waterproof
✅Smudge-proof, transfer-proof, flake-proof
✅SO easy to remove
❌Doesn’t bleed

I cannot wait to see all of the amazing liner looks you guys are going to create with Life Liner Quick N Easy. Love you all so much! #Launching5August on hudabeauty.com & retailers 17 Aug

RELATED VID: https://youtu.be/M8PHYl1NWpU 
TANTOUR: https://www.shophudabeauty.com/default/tantour 
MORE INFO: http://bit.ly/2PN1Ofo 

***For best results*** 

STEP 1: Using the smaller side of the Huda Beauty Sculpt & Shade brush, apply Tantour in dots along the contours of each side of the face: cheekbones, forehead, and jawline.

STEP 2: With the fluffy side of the brush or using a beauty sponge, blend well for an all-over healthy finish. You can build to desired intensity.

My tip: Use the brush in circular, upward motions for a flawless finish!

***

The Tantour collection consists of the following rich and creamy shades:

Fair: a neutral honey shade, recommend for fair to light complexions
Light: a soft caramel shade, recommended for light to medium complexions
Medium: a neutral mocha shade, recommended for medium to tan complexions
Tan: a deep cocoa shade, recommended for deep tan to rich complexions 
Rich: a deep mahogany shade, recommended for rich to ultra-rich complexions

title: How to Remove Hair Easily - Simple Tips for Hair Removal!
description:
My personal experience with Hair Removal 

Hey my loves! If there’s one thing that I always get asked about, it’s hair removal. Thanks to my Middle Eastern heritage, I have naturally very thick, dark hair, and I’ve always been very open about it. I’ve literally tried every form of hair removal treatment possible from laser hair removal to waxing to shaving to face shaving! So, I thought I’d do a quick video answering all of your questions, and share ALL my hair removal tips with you guys!

On a side note hair removal is a very personal thing and if you don’t feel like you want to remove your hair, that’s totally fine too. I prefer my body to be hair free, but like I said, that’s my personal choice. Thanks so much for watching, love you guys!

title: How to Shave Your Face (and why it's AWESOME!) | حلاقة الوجه مفيدة للنساء؟
description:
Okay my loves, so I know this is going to sound weird, but yes I shave my face! Whhhhy? Well I read years ago about so many beauty icons who did, so I thought I would try it, and I loved it! I have lasered areas that have slightly thicker hair, and def recommend that for areas around the mouth and chin, and side burns, but if you have areas where the hair is super thin and more like peach fuzz, you may find this is your best bet! 

Now I recommend doing it on dry clean skin, and with short gentle movements. I find when its on dry skin, it doesn't grow back thicker and really works best! I saw these razors everywhere in South Korea last week, and I have found mine from Amazon, I love them!
